Implemented the filter tank controller state machine in:

- `components/controller/controller.c`

Also added visible firmware-level self-tests in:

- `agent_tests/test_filter_tank_sequence.py`

What’s covered:
- boot-safe idle behavior
- gating until both sensors are valid
- filtering → settling → draining → complete flow
- settle timing and early-drain prevention
- disturbance recovery in settling and draining
- malformed input and sensor timeout safe fallback
- UART end-to-end probes via `FirmwareSession`

